cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with clustering using deep autoencoders, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on deep learning and clustering, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.CV and cs.AI. The other two sub-categories are less likely but still possible since the paper deals with unsupervised learning and could potentially involve natural language processing or evolutionary computing techniques.
